Sentencas: Sr0.25Bi0.5FeO3 (delta) (SBF) has been studied as a cathode material for low- and intermediate-temperature (600-850 degreesC) solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) based on the La0.9Sr0.9Ga0.9Mg0.1O3 (LSGM) electrolyte.
Titulo: Electrocatalytic properties of an Sr0.25Bi0.5FeO3-δ/LSGM interface
